<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><a><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi&nbsp;</span></a><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">{!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">You elected to pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!Policy__c.Name}</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;through direct debit payments.&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance require you to consent to the commission Kingsbridge receive in order to provide the loan for your insurance policy.&nbsp;</b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Close Brothers are sending you communications via email, SMS and physical letter to notify you of this requirement. This is to provide you with the steps required to provide consent.&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.closebrotherspf.com/customers/finance-application">You can learn more and consent here</a>.</b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><u>You need to provide consent within the deadline provided by Close Brothers in order for your premium finance agreement to be accepted.<br></u></b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If Close Brothers reject your credit application the payment for your insurance policy would remain outstanding.&nbsp;</b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you have any queries about this process, please call us on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;to discuss further.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Kind regards,</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>